metadata.name: Queen of the Sea #1/7
metadata.description:
Queen of the Sea is a mesmerizing depiction of a mermaid exuding the essence of Venus, the goddess of beauty and harmony. Her mischievous eyes and alluring charm captivate the viewer, drawing them into her world. The piece radiates with an otherworldly aura, evoking a sense of wonder and enchantment.

## !AR Artwork!

Each holder (both primary and secondary) can claim a magnetic postcard with the piece for the best AR experience.
